Package: leri
Title: Access Landscape Evaporative Response Index (LERI) Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Max",
           family = "Joseph",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "maxwell.b.joseph@colorado.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7745-9990"))
Description: Acquire and work with Landscape Evaporative
    Response Index (LERI) data programmatically. This package provides
    utilities for downloading and reading LERI raster data. More info on
    LERI is avaiable at <https://www.esrl.noaa.gov/psd/leri/>.
